# 🎯 Real-Time Guessing Game

A real-time multiplayer guessing game built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **Socket.IO**.
Players can join a game session, compete to guess the correct answer, and track scores live.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎮 Create and join game sessions
- 👥 Real-time multiplayer (Socket.IO)
- 🧑‍🏫 Dynamic Game Master rotation
- ❓ Custom questions and answers
- ⏱️ Timed game rounds (60 seconds)
- 🎯 3 attempts per player
- 🏆 Score tracking system
- 📊 Live player updates
- 🚫 Prevent joining during active game
- 🔄 Automatic session reset after each round

---

## 🧠 How It Works

1. A player creates a session and becomes the **Game Master**
2. Other players join using the session ID
3. Game Master sets a question and answer
4. Game starts when there are at least **3 players**
5. Players attempt to guess the answer (max 3 tries)
6. Game ends when:
   - A player guesses correctly ✅
   - Time runs out ⏰

7. Scores are updated and a new Game Master is assigned

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Real-time Communication:** Socket.IO
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, Vanilla JavaScript
- **State Management:** In-memory (JavaScript objects)

