---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone the repository

```
git clone https://github.com/olaplentymoney/GuessingGame.git
cd GuessingGame
```

---

### 2. Install dependencies

```
npm install
```

---

### 3. Run the server

```
node server/server.js
```

---

### 4. Open in browser

```
http://localhost:3000
```

---

## 🎮 Usage

- Enter your name
- Create a game session or join using a session ID
- If you are the Game Master:
  - Set a question and answer
  - Start the game

- If you are a player:
  - Submit guesses
  - Track your score

---

## 📌 Key Concepts Demonstrated

- Event-driven architecture
- WebSockets & real-time communication
- State management without a database
- Multiplayer session handling
- Backend-controlled game logic

---

## ⚠️ Limitations

- Uses in-memory storage (data resets on server restart)
- No authentication system
- Basic UI (focused on functionality)

---

## 🚀 Future Improvements

- Add database (MongoDB/PostgreSQL)
- Implement user authentication
- Improve UI/UX (React frontend)
- Add chat system
- Deploy online (Render / Railway / Vercel)

